Lingua/RU/Antimat version 1.00
==============================


Lingua::RU::Antimat - Perl Module for removal Russian slang from chat, guestbooks, etc.

Check Lingua::RU::Antimat web site at http://www.tcen.ru/antimat. 
There you will find Russian documentation, tutorial, etc.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

FileHandle

